pullRequest.title: iOS Fixes and Formatting.
pullRequest.bodyText:
Fix for process response where some default values were saving when user skips the step.
Fix for refresh token.
Update swift-format
Change in delete account.
Fix in ResearchKit for Question Selection state.
Added description for passcode setup UI.

commit.message:
- Update anchor act response & delete account  API.
- Fix process response with skip steps & refresh token.

- Show description to set passcode.
- Update swift-format.

afterCommit.message:
- Show description to set passcode.
- Update swift-format.

nodes.bodyText: nit: it's better to not repeat a property in its name, i.e. study.name reads better than study.studyName
